flog.appender           Manage appenders for loggers
flog.carp               Always return the log message
flog.layout             Manage layouts within the 'futile.logger'
                        sub-system
flog.logger             Manage loggers
flog.remove             Remove a logger
flog.threshold          Get and set the threshold for a logger
ftry                    Wrap a try block in futile.logger
futile.logger-package   A Logging Utility for R
logger.options          Constants for 'futile.logger'
scat                    Print formatted messages
